author: Echo_Fennec💛💙
text:
Your pretty face,
the way you talk, the way you smile.
Hey tunnel vision, welcome back,
it's been a while.
I wanna hold your stupid hand,
 and kiss your stupid face.
Who knew agony could be a little fun?✨

author: Echo_Fennec💛💙
text:
I grew tough cuz love, it only hurt me back,
but loving you is a good problem to have.
I'm use to that, but I could get use to this.
You're the pink in my cheeks and I love that in me,
cuz I'm a little bit soft

author: Echo_Fennec💛💙
text:
I know we'll never grow old together,
cuz you'll never grow old to me.
You're the pink in my cheeks and I'm scared
cuz that means I'm a little bit soft.

author: Echo_Fennec💛💙
text:
Slow dance with you.
I just wanna slow dance with you.
Why don't you take the chance I've got the moves,
I'd like to prove, I wanna,
slow dance with you.

author: Echo_Fennec💛💙
text: There's something terrifyingly beautiful in not knowing what will happen next

author: Echo_Fennec💛💙
text:
I spoke to you in cautious tones,
you answered me with no pretense.
And still I feel I've said too much,
my silence is my self defense.

So I would choose to be with you,
as if the choice were mine to make.
But you can make decisions too,
and you can have this heart to break🎶
